properties.name: The Belfry Golf Club
properties.description: Posted by 247golfer Wishaw B76 9PR , Birmingham, UKOne of the worlds most famous golf destinations, a visit to The De Vere Belfry is a must for any one with a passion for the game of golf. There are three courses to enjoy. Whether you are new to the beautiful game or have been hooked for years we have something for everyone to take pleasure from. The De Vere Belfry is home to the Quinn Direct British Masters, and has hosted the Benson & Hedges International Open and the PGA Seniors\' Championship. Such high credentials are testimony to the quality of golf you will experience at The De Vere Belfry. It is this quality that has also led to The De Vere Belfry being chosen as home to the headquarters of The PGA of Great Britain & Ireland, The PGA of Europe, and the PGA National Training Academy.
